 2023-01182023-02-10PSPC, NCC
ActNational Capital Act
SubjectOrder Approving that National Capital Commission Extend the Lease with the Innovation Centre at Bayview Yards
PrecisOrder approving that National Capital Commission grant two options to extend the lease with the the INNOVATION CENTRE AT BAYVIEW YARDS for (1) a period of five years, beginning on February 1, 2024, for the real property located at Building 400, 1740 Woodroffe Avenue, in Ottawa, Ontario; and (2) a period of two years, beginning on January 1, 2026, for real property located at Building 401, 1740 Woodroffe Avenue, in Ottawa, Ontario.
